{
  "stem": "15732.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With the ending of the war, a new chapter started which was called repatriation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Repatriation of all those people that were dislocated, were sent away, by the Germans, or taken away, in different parts of Europe.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They dislocated the whole of-- of Europe, where Jews are concerned or what the other minorities that they-- one, for instance, gypsies-- that they dislocated.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what-- what affected us was that my father being-- having-- having been a Polish citizen, and I still had that passport that were-- we were under Swiss protectorate, we could have-- we could go back to Poland as-- with the repatriation.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That meant that we would escape Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That meant for the last time of finishing of the chapter Cernauti.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Leaving-- leaving again, with a rucksack, in peacetime so-- so to speak, after the war, but leaving Cernauti.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it was under Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And under no circumstances did we want to live under communist rule.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the-- in August, 1945.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That were a few months after-- we went-- after end of the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went with a cattle wagon through Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was one of the most memorable things that happened to me was we were sitting in the wagon and passing by-- that I assume it was Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I assume.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not so sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we saw peasants digging, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and bones and craniums?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Skulls.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Skulls.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Skulls.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Skulls.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And skulls were just flying, were coming out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you-- you saw them sitting-- there were masses of peasants, digging out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were just flying, all those-- those bones and those cranium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all I felt were, who knows, who knows who they are.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And most probably, they are Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
